    <p>The following default transformation scenarios are available for individual DITA topics:<ul>
        <li><uicontrol>DITA XHTML</uicontrol> - Transforms a DITA topic to XHTML using DITA Open
          Toolkit.</li>
        <li><uicontrol>DITA PDF</uicontrol> - Transforms a DITA topic to PDF using the DITA Open
          Toolkit and the Apache FOP engine.</li>
      </ul></p>
